## Decisions and Action Items

| Proposal / Draft | Dispatch Outcome | Action Item |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **TTTPS: Pre-Ingestion Proof of Time** (`draft-jorgan-tttps`) | **No IETF Action** | The author may pursue the Independent Submissions Editor (ISE) track on their own. The IETF will take no direct action. |
| **Secured Digital Lifecycle Protocol** (`draft-norton-sdlp`) | **No IETF Action** | The author was advised to look at external industry efforts (such as Sigstore, SCITT, or iota.org). |
| **CIRP: Capability-Oriented Intent Routing Protocol** (`draft-verma-chirp-routing`) | **No IETF Action** | The author should work on building a multi-party community of interest and split the architecture into focused drafts. |
| **DNS-Based Agent Naming (DAN)** (`draft-seethiraju-dan-agent-naming`) | **Direct to Working Group** | Route the proposal to the **DAN Working Group** for further development. |

